Desert Wind (Stance) [Fire]
Level: Swordsage 1
Initiation Action: 1 swift action
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: Stance

You gain some resistance to fire as long as you remain in this stance. The amount of resistance is determined by your ranks in Tumble. Four to eight ranks in Tumble grants five Fire Resistance.  Nine to thirteen grants ten Fire Resistance.  Fourteen to eighteen grants twenty Fire Resistance.  If you have 19 or more ranks in Tumble, you gain immunity to fire while you are in this stance.

This stance is a supernatural ability.